{"tid":1580072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共新規：記者要熟讀習思想 考試肥佬無得撈","createTime":"2019-09-19T01:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T02:16:52.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad10f5e79bbef340a448827c9e3def66e9fcf92c","tid":1580072,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190918/large/1568797043_0cd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568797043_0cd2.jpg&h=0fd26cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地媒體報道，中共中宣部較早前公佈新規定，今年將透過「學習強國」手機App，對全國新聞編採人員展開在線崗位培訓考試，記者必須通過包括「習思想」等內容的考試，才能申領新版記者證。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，中宣部傳媒監管局8月23日發出「關於在『學習強國』學習平台創建和認證新聞採編學習組織的通知」，其中對新聞單位申領新版新聞記者證作出具體要求。<br />\n<br />\n根據通知，申領者須通過「學習強國」平台手機用戶端的培訓考試，通過後才能申領新版記者證。考試內容包括：習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想、習近平總書記關於宣傳思想工作的重要講話、馬克思主義新聞觀、新聞倫理與政策法規以及新聞採編業務。<br />\n<br />\n據最新消息，本月底會有一批單位進行「試點考試」，而正式考試初定於10月上旬，採閉卷方式。考試不合格者，可獲再安排考試，但只能補考一次。<br />\n<br />\n此外，各新聞單位須在「學習強國」學習平台完成新聞採編學習組織的創建和認證，否則無法參加考試和申領新版新聞記者證。<br />\n<br />\n「學習強國」是由中共中央宣傳部主管、以中共總書記習近平的講話和「習思想」為主要內容的「理論學習平台」，包括網站和手機App，今年1月初上線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190918/60057999?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60057999%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5cF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ea621f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60057999%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=aaacee2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190918/60057999?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9ffdeab46822e4932449452e474ffab6fd445e3b","tid":1580072,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"讀囉<br />\nPass左之後鳩理"},{"pid":"57fc0db73c1e1591f13aee4f72821f3f44c27dab","tid":1580072,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"真係chinazi CLS"},{"pid":"359ac8e1612958ae35245648a810efbd7aeeeb18","tid":1580072,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"a86ebfab4c88aef3052ce921eb7f16ce6ad41d9c","tid":1580072,"uid":7818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"個app真係叫學習強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753e8e249fe2a4ca95afbb11ad6fcc787c707ad5","tid":1580072,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ffdeab46822e4932449452e474ffab6fd445e3b","tid":1580072,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"讀囉<br />\nPass左之後鳩理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"唔理即炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cc96ef99d0c6f9d0b7780d5847389ba8231e36","tid":1580072,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:59:23.000Z","msg":"學習強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efc295fdbfeedf93bff6cffe6eb7b6d786941b5","tid":1580072,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"赤納粹巨大國家機器<img src=\"/as